<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 06:11:23 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>在内塔尼亚胡看来，以色列人质绝不是一种资产</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-21/ty-article/.premium/as-far-as-netanyahu-is-concerned-the-hostages-are-anything-but-an-asset/00000191-71c7-dabe-a597-fbef42bb0000</link><description>总理正在就释放人质进行谈判，却没有考虑谁应该对他们的被囚禁负责，就好像他们走错了方向，最终进入了加沙的隧道一样。虽然辩方正在谈论价值观，但对他来说只有一个价值观很重要：生存</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 03:00:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-21/ty-article/.premium/as-far-as-netanyahu-is-concerned-the-hostages-are-anything-but-an-asset/00000191-71c7-dabe-a597-fbef42bb0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军称，黎巴嫩火箭弹袭击了以色列戈兰高地；一人被弹片轻伤，多间房屋被击中</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-21/ty-article-live/report-idf-attacks-deep-inside-lebanon-after-dozens-of-rockets-fired-at-northern-israel/00000191-72b6-d5c0-afb3-f3f7bdf00000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡对协议表示怀疑，坚称以色列控制加沙-埃及边境；哈马斯批评美国提议 ■ 以色列国防军称从黎巴嫩发射了 100 多枚火箭弹和无人机；一些被拦截，另一些倒在空旷地区。 ■ 拜登：“全天候”致力于加沙停火、人质协议。 ■ 埃及外长称，停火谈判将于周四和周五在开罗举行；以色列消息人士称日期尚未确定 ■ 伊朗革命卫队发言人表示，伊朗报复的等待期“可能很长”</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 02:24:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-21/ty-article-live/report-idf-attacks-deep-inside-lebanon-after-dozens-of-rockets-fired-at-northern-israel/00000191-72b6-d5c0-afb3-f3f7bdf00000</guid></item><item><title>民主党人相信，无论特朗普和共和党怎么说，犹太人的选票坚定地对他们有利</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-08-21/ty-article/.premium/democrats-believe-the-jewish-vote-is-solidly-in-their-favor-no-matter-what-trump-says/00000191-725a-d8ab-a1f5-7a7e456a0000</link><description>一位研究犹太投票模式的专家表示，“犹太选民毫不犹豫地表示，批评以色列政府政策并仍然支持以色列是可以的”</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 00:51:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-08-21/ty-article/.premium/democrats-believe-the-jewish-vote-is-solidly-in-their-favor-no-matter-what-trump-says/00000191-725a-d8ab-a1f5-7a7e456a0000</guid></item><item><title>参与停火谈判的消息人士称内塔尼亚胡“再次破坏谈判”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-20/ty-article/sources-involved-in-cease-fire-negotiations-say-netanyahu-is-once-again-sabotaging-talks/00000191-7168-dadb-a1f9-7dfb63870000</link><description>一位消息人士称，总理在会见死者家属时的言论“使达成协议变得更加困难，增加了怀疑，并向哈马斯和调解人发出信号，表明内塔尼亚胡对达成协议不感兴趣。”本周在埃及举行的峰会日期尚未确定</description><pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 20:55:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-20/ty-article/sources-involved-in-cease-fire-negotiations-say-netanyahu-is-once-again-sabotaging-talks/00000191-7168-dadb-a1f9-7dfb63870000</guid></item><item><title>以色列央行行长敦促内塔尼亚胡因延迟问题启动2025年预算</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-20/ty-article/.premium/bank-of-israel-governor-urges-netanyahu-to-start-the-2025-budget-amid-delay-concerns/00000191-7126-dadb-a1f9-7dff19fa0000</link><description>鉴于最近举行的预算会议没有专业公务员的充分参与，以色列央行行长阿米尔·亚龙教授致信内塔尼亚胡，对推迟批准明年的预算表示担忧</description><pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 20:36:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-20/ty-article/.premium/bank-of-israel-governor-urges-netanyahu-to-start-the-2025-budget-amid-delay-concerns/00000191-7126-dadb-a1f9-7dff19fa0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列袭击学校和市场，造成至少 20 名巴勒斯坦人死亡，其中包括儿童</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-20/ty-article/at-least-20-palestinians-including-children-killed-in-israeli-strikes-on-school-market/00000191-70fd-d8ab-a1f5-7afd080d0000</link><description>代尔巴拉赫市场罢工现场的目击者称，大多数伤亡者是儿童。以色列国防军在评论造成 12 人死亡的学校袭击事件时表示，袭击目标是哈马斯指挥中心</description><pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 20:04:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-20/ty-article/at-least-20-palestinians-including-children-killed-in-israeli-strikes-on-school-market/00000191-70fd-d8ab-a1f5-7afd080d0000</guid></item><item><title>芝加哥人质广场：家庭、亲以色列团体在民主党全国委员会外集会“反对所有仇恨者”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-08-20/ty-article/.premium/hostage-square-chicago-families-pro-israel-group-rally-outside-dnc-against-all-haters/00000191-712c-d7fc-ab93-f33f2d6f0000</link><description>由以色列美国委员会组织的多媒体“人质广场”展览包括与在加沙被扣押的以色列和美国人质的家人的谈话，以及旨在反映 10 月 7 日恐怖事件的艺术作品</description><pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 19:53:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-08-20/ty-article/.premium/hostage-square-chicago-families-pro-israel-group-rally-outside-dnc-against-all-haters/00000191-712c-d7fc-ab93-f33f2d6f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列总检察长表示，应总理妻子的要求，国家不应资助内塔尼亚胡的别墅泳池翻修工程</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-20/ty-article/.premium/ag-says-state-shouldnt-fund-netanyahus-villa-pool-renovation-amid-pms-wifes-request/00000191-70c6-d988-a3b5-71eec8b90000</link><description>总检察长发表上述意见之前，以色列议会的一个委员会推动了内塔尼亚胡家族在凯撒利亚和耶路撒冷私人住宅的开支大幅扩大融资规模。</description><pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 18:09:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-20/ty-article/.premium/ag-says-state-shouldnt-fund-netanyahus-villa-pool-renovation-amid-pms-wifes-request/00000191-70c6-d988-a3b5-71eec8b90000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡活埋人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-20/ty-article/.highlight/netanyahu-is-burying-the-hostages-alive/00000191-7058-d1e1-af95-73d9890c0000</link><description>以色列军队周二从加沙南部的一个隧道中打捞出六名人质的尸体，并将他们送回以色列埋葬。虽然过去将人质带回家的行动被誉为希望的迹象，但这一次却让人感到沉默和阴沉</description><pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 18:08:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-20/ty-article/.highlight/netanyahu-is-burying-the-hostages-alive/00000191-7058-d1e1-af95-73d9890c0000</guid></item><item><title>达美航空暂停飞往以色列的航班直至 9 月 30 日；哪些航空公司仍在运营？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-20/ty-article/.premium/delta-suspends-flights-to-israel-until-september-30-which-airlines-are-still-flying/00000191-70ba-d7fc-ab93-f2bf4c4f0000</link><description>一些航空公司已取消飞往特拉维夫的航班直至 2025 年春季，但其他航空公司在真主党和伊朗的威胁导致安全担忧升级后已恢复航班</description><pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 18:01:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-20/ty-article/.premium/delta-suspends-flights-to-israel-until-september-30-which-airlines-are-still-flying/00000191-70ba-d7fc-ab93-f2bf4c4f0000</guid></item><item><title>再次受骗：美国以某种方式听到内塔尼亚胡对加沙协议说“是”。他没有</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-08-20/ty-article/.premium/duped-again-the-u-s-somehow-heard-netanyahu-say-yes-to-a-gaza-deal-he-didnt/00000191-7008-d7fc-ab93-f23f3f6e0000</link><description>美国正在以新的紧迫感推动达成协议，试图在 11 月总统大选前避免地区冲突。但未来几天将表明美国是否准备好使用其在过去 10 个月中选择不使用的影响力杠杆</description><pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 17:22:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-08-20/ty-article/.premium/duped-again-the-u-s-somehow-heard-netanyahu-say-yes-to-a-gaza-deal-he-didnt/00000191-7008-d7fc-ab93-f23f3f6e0000</guid></item><item><title>现在已经很清楚了：内塔尼亚胡宁愿把人质装在尸袋里，也不愿拿自己的政治生命去冒险</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-20/ty-article/.premium/its-now-clear-netanyahu-prefers-hostages-in-body-bags-over-risking-his-political-life/00000191-707e-d180-a5f5-707fc4490000</link><description>解救死去的人质是以色列政府的选择：它避免让步，并防止人质透露有关他们被囚禁或国家放弃的细节 ■ 内塔尼亚胡坚定地保留对加沙主要路线的控制并恢复战斗，向哈马斯领导人辛瓦尔发出信号：不达成协议</description><pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 16:40:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-20/ty-article/.premium/its-now-clear-netanyahu-prefers-hostages-in-body-bags-over-risking-his-political-life/00000191-707e-d180-a5f5-707fc4490000</guid></item><item><title>以色列处于战争状态，第 319 天：前以色列国防军司令称，内塔尼亚胡带领我们陷入了伊朗的陷阱“辛瓦尔”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-20/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-319-netanyahu-led-us-into-sinwar-irans-trap-ex-idf-chief-says/00000191-7068-db7d-a7d7-7ce8108c0001</link><description>10 月 7 日，以色列国防军打捞出被哈马斯活捉的 6 名人质尸体 ■ 以色列国防军表示，以色列的空袭可能导致部分人质死亡 ■ 前埃及外交官表示，加沙休战谈判将于周四在开罗恢复 ■ 人质的母亲称以色列摩萨德酋长告诉她，“在当前的政治形势下”，人质交易是不可能的。 ■ 战争已经过去 319 天了，你需要知道的就是这些</description><pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 16:31:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-20/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-319-netanyahu-led-us-into-sinwar-irans-trap-ex-idf-chief-says/00000191-7068-db7d-a7d7-7ce8108c0001</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦西岸居民被控谋杀以色列监狱工作人员</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-20/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-west-bank-resident-to-be-charged-with-murder-of-israel-prison-service-worker/00000191-702e-d1e1-af95-73af8ec10000</link><description>约海·阿夫尼 (Yohai Avni) 在吉文·哈哈达沙 (Givon Hahadasha) 定居点的家中被杀，几周后嫌疑人承认了谋杀案。尽管袭击没有任何政治动机，但这名巴勒斯坦人现在被列为安全囚犯</description><pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 15:14:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-20/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-west-bank-resident-to-be-charged-with-murder-of-israel-prison-service-worker/00000191-702e-d1e1-af95-73af8ec10000</guid></item><item><title>“殉难归来”：哈马斯威胁发动更多自杀式袭击，“工程师”叶海亚·阿亚什 (Yahya Ayyash) 趋于流行</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-08-20/ty-article/.premium/the-engineer-yahya-ayyash-trends-as-hamas-threatens-more-suicide-attacks/00000191-700e-dab0-a9b7-f41ebf440000</link><description>阿亚什因在巴以冲突中引入自杀性爆炸而臭名昭著，1996 年被以色列杀害，在特拉维夫发生爆炸未遂事件后，阿亚什再次受到关注</description><pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 14:37:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-08-20/ty-article/.premium/the-engineer-yahya-ayyash-trends-as-hamas-threatens-more-suicide-attacks/00000191-700e-dab0-a9b7-f41ebf440000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队兵力短缺，征召先前获得豁免但认为适合服役的预备役人员</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-20/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-calls-up-reservists-previously-given-exemptions-to-fill-personnel-shortage/00000191-6fee-d7fc-ab93-efff29ba0000</link><description>陆军官员表示，“作为以色列国防军扩大现役士兵人数计划的一部分”，大约 15,000 名士兵（全部在 35 岁以下）已分三轮被征召入伍。</description><pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 14:22:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-20/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-calls-up-reservists-previously-given-exemptions-to-fill-personnel-shortage/00000191-6fee-d7fc-ab93-efff29ba0000</guid></item><item><title>残酷的回忆：哈马斯在特拉维夫发动的自杀式爆炸是对加沙的回应</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-08-20/ty-article/.premium/a-grim-flashback-suicide-bombing-by-hamas-in-tel-aviv-was-a-response-to-gaza/00000191-6fcc-d1e1-af95-7fcd69fe0000</link><description>哈马斯认为，许多达成协议的提议是一个陷阱，美国将采取以色列拒绝结束战争和从加沙地带撤军的立场</description><pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 14:04:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-08-20/ty-article/.premium/a-grim-flashback-suicide-bombing-by-hamas-in-tel-aviv-was-a-response-to-gaza/00000191-6fcc-d1e1-af95-7fcd69fe0000</guid></item><item><title>国际学生联合会将以色列踢出局：“伊朗、俄罗斯和叙利亚仍然存在”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2024-08-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/intl-student-federation-kicks-israelis-out-iran-russia-and-syria-are-still-there/00000191-6b0b-dc6e-a991-ebff69ed0000</link><description>在没有文件和任何书面决定的情况下，以色列代表被国际医学生协会联合会暂停资格。在此之前发生的事情应该引起人们对以色列在世界地位崩溃的警惕</description><pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 11:55:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2024-08-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/intl-student-federation-kicks-israelis-out-iran-russia-and-syria-are-still-there/00000191-6b0b-dc6e-a991-ebff69ed0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列针对伊朗大规模窃取秘密数据的战争进行了徒劳的战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-08-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israels-futile-war-against-massive-iranian-hack-of-secret-data/00000191-6bd7-d1ee-afb5-6bff8a510000</link><description>反以色列黑客窃取了大量以色列敏感数据，现在正在发布数十亿字节的秘密和机密信息。由于无法阻止黑客攻击，以色列正在发动一场徒劳的战争来阻止泄密</description><pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 11:19:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-08-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israels-futile-war-against-massive-iranian-hack-of-secret-data/00000191-6bd7-d1ee-afb5-6bff8a510000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军方打捞出哈马斯囚禁期间被杀的六名人质尸体，亲属猛烈抨击内塔尼亚胡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-20/ty-article/.premium/israel-retrieves-bodies-of-6-hostages-killed-in-hamas-captivity-relatives-slam-netanyahu/00000191-6ef2-d87e-a9b3-6ffb2b1c0000</link><description>人质在加沙全部死亡，他们的家人指责政府抛弃他们，并呼吁紧急释放其余人质</description><pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 09:18:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-20/ty-article/.premium/israel-retrieves-bodies-of-6-hostages-killed-in-hamas-captivity-relatives-slam-netanyahu/00000191-6ef2-d87e-a9b3-6ffb2b1c0000</guid></item></channel></rss>